    "description": "<strong>Thebes</strong> is a 1v1 multiplayer strategy game set in an environment inspired by the paintings of Giorgio de Chirico. The objective is to utilize pieces with different abilities to navigate through the <strong>fog of war</strong> and destroy the enemy fortress.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/cbbf4614635692e9fbcd2e591e5077ad.poster.avif?t=1723818298\" width=584 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/cbbf4614635692e9fbcd2e591e5077ad.webm?t=1723818298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/cbbf4614635692e9fbcd2e591e5077ad.mp4?t=1723818298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each piece has <strong>different abilities</strong> and varying patterns of <strong>vision</strong> or <strong>attack</strong>. Find the right strategy to surprise your enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/9d2e80ac3e88c94ff5e6c8becde32663.poster.avif?t=1723818298\" width=462 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/9d2e80ac3e88c94ff5e6c8becde32663.webm?t=1723818298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009890/extras/9d2e80ac3e88c94ff5e6c8becde32663.mp4?t=1723818298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each turn, you have a limited number of points to spend on actions, including:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spawning new pieces.<br></li><li>Moving or attacking.<br></li><li>Activating abilities.</li></ul><br>Keep an eye on as many cells as possible; the fog can conceal an enemy piece, which could be fatal.",
